name: Token
description: The Token contract is suited for creating a digital currency and is compliant with the ERC20 standard.

name: StakeERC721
description: This contract allows users to stake their ERC-721 NFTs and get ERC-20 tokens as staking rewards.

name: Marketplace
description: A Marketplace is a contract where you can buy and sell NFTs, such as OpenSea or Rarible.

name: NFT Drop
description: The NFT Drop contract is ideal when you want to release a collection of unique NFTs using the ERC721A Standard.
